04/04/2003
TIRANA, Albania -- Parliament endorsed an agreement with Greece Thursday (3 April on reconstruction of the Bishtpalla naval base on the Adriatic Sea. Under the terms of the deal, Athens will rebuild the base, at a cost of some 5.5m euros. Lengthy debate preceded the vote; opponents argued that existing law bars such agreements. (Albanian Daily News - 04/04/03; ATA - 03/04/03)
